## ⚙️ Setup Environment

### 1. Create virtual environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

### 2. Activate

* Windows:

```powershell
venv\Scripts\activate
```

* macOS / Linux:

```bash
source venv/bin/activate
```

---

### 3. Install dependencies

#### 👉 CPU

```bash
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r invoice_ocr/requirements.txt
```

#### 👉 GPU (recommended for production)

```bash
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r invoice_ocr/requirements-gpt.txt
```

> ⚠️ Ensure CUDA + PyTorch compatibility if using GPU

---

## 🤖 Model Setup

⚠️ Models **KHÔNG được commit trong repo**

Bạn cần:

* Copy từ internal storage / server
* Hoặc download từ nguồn được cung cấp

### Set Environment Variables

#### Windows (PowerShell)

```powershell
$env:MODEL_PATH_HEADER="C:\path\to\model_final_header\final_model"
$env:MODEL_PATH_TABLE="C:\path\to\model_final_table\final_model"
$env:MODEL_PATH_FOOTER="C:\path\to\model_final_footer\final_model"
```

#### Linux / macOS

```bash
export MODEL_PATH_HEADER=/path/to/model_final_header/final_model
export MODEL_PATH_TABLE=/path/to/model_final_table/final_model
export MODEL_PATH_FOOTER=/path/to/model_final_footer/final_model
```

